#define MMWAVE_MAX_PROFILE   4
 mmWave Supported max profiles which can be configured on the BSS
 
#define MMWAVE_ACK_TIMEOUT   1000U
 This is the ACK wait timeout in msec. This is the time for which the mmWave link module will wait for the reception on an ACK from the BSS. If this is set to 0 then the mmWave link will not wait for an ACK.

Detailed Description

This is the high level API which is used to abstract the mmWave link API and allow application developers to be abstracted from the lower level complexities.
